OL,3,CProlific shoplifter who targeted Co-op
OL,4,Cstores jailed
OL,6,FA shoplifter who stole alcohol,
OL,7,Fcigarettes and tobacco from a number
OL,8,Fof Co-op stores in Reading has been
OL,9,Fjailed for sixteen months.
OL,11,FBetween March and June 2024, Simon
OL,12,FHawkins, 36, of no fixed address,
OL,13,Ftargeted shops on Overdown Road and
OL,14,FSouth View Avenue.
OL,16,FHe was arrested on 22 June and was
OL,17,Fcharged the following day.
