OL,3,CProlific shoplifter who targeted Co-op
OL,4,Cstores jailed
OL,6,FOn Monday 30 September, Hawkins was
OL,7,Fsentenced at Reading Crown Court for
OL,8,Ffour counts of burglary non-dwelling
OL,9,Fand three counts of shoplifting.
OL,11,FCCTV from one of the Co-op stores
OL,12,Fshows Hawkins raiding the draws of the
OL,13,Ftobacco kiosk before fleeing the scene.
OL,15,FThames Valley Police said the sentence
OL,16,Fis just one result of 'Operation
OL,17,FPurchase', a programme targeting the
OL,18,Fmost prolific offenders.
