OL,6,FPC Vince Moore said: "Simon Hawkins
OL,7,Fwas a prolific shoplifter in Reading
OL,8,Ftown centre and I am pleased he is now
OL,9,Fbehind bars.
OL,11,F"I hope this ruling sends a clear
OL,12,Fmessage to shoplifters that your
OL,13,Fbehaviour will not be tolerated and
OL,14,Fyou will be brought to justice."
